## Additional Terms for Educational and Research Use

This software is provided as an educational and research demonstration platform
for computational drug discovery. The prediction methods included are for
demonstrational purposes only and should not be used for:

1. Clinical decision-making
2. Regulatory submission without proper validation
3. Production pharmaceutical R&D without replacing heuristic functions with
   validated QSAR models

Users are responsible for:
- Validating any methods before production use
- Ensuring compliance with applicable regulations (FDA, EMA, etc.)
- Proper citation of scientific methods (see REFERENCES.md)

The author and contributors make no claims regarding the accuracy, reliability,
or suitability of this software for any particular purpose. All predictions
should be experimentally validated.
